---
title: Chorizo, Capsicum & Crumbly Cheese Shakshuka with Sourdough & Rocket
description: Take a bite of Middle Eastern decadence with our chorizo shakshuka and crunchy sourdough. Enjoy the taste of our creamy
crumbly cheese combined with chorizo and capsicum mixed into a rich tomato sauce. With everything cooked in one pan, all you
need to do is add your eggs and enjoy!
